headline.main: Brandon Marshall Is Expected to Join Growing List of Jets’ Castoffs
headline.print_headline: Marshall Is Expected to Join Growing List of Jets’ Castoffs

lead_paragraph: Alexis Peterson made four 3-pointers and scored 29 points and 21st-ranked Syracuse defeated North Carolina 83-64 in the second round of the ACC Tournament on Saturday night.
